dct_description_sm: Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
3 bar scales on map given in "Lieues francaise", "Lieues astronomiques", and "Lieues d'Allemagne".
Shows topography, drainage, places of historical interest.
Inset map: Description du Mont Liban et du Kesroan.
